  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">NCT Crisis Modifier ZRBF BRACT 2018-19</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Protection of the fragile resilience gains that vulnerable individuals, households and communities in category B1 and B2 have made over the past year and beyond</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project provides a practical means to avert or reduce the impact of the looming below average rainfall as a result of the EL NINO effect on beneficiaries&#x2019; production and productivity whilst protecting resilience gains made by communities as a result of ZRBF BRACT and other efforts. The project provides market based input support to increase production of drought tolerant crops, rehabilitate community irrigation schemes and water harvesting infrastructure to improve and diversify crop production as well improve access to food, feed and water.</narrative>
  </description>
